<HL>
   Unisys Earnings
   Plummeted 78%
   In 2nd Quarter
   ----
   By Laurence Hooper
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C9
</SO>
